
  Slakoth    Normal Type Pokémon

  SLAKOTH lolls around for over 
  twenty hours every day.  Because 
  it moves so little, it does not 
  need much food.  Slakoth’s 
  sole daily meal consists of just 
  three leaves. 
	   Evolution Chain
  Slakoth ► Vigoroth ► Slaking

